data.description: Introducing a fantastic investment opportunity, 5127 Greene Lane is situated in the highly sought-after Strip/University submarket. This fourplex includes one 3-bedroom, one 2-bedroom, & two 1-bedroom units. Each unit comes with its own private single-car garage, ensuring convenience and security for residents. Great opportunity for owner-occupant FHA buyer, the 1bd units are mo/mo. The location is incredibly advantageous, being positioned within a mere two-mile radius of notable landmarks such as the University of Nevada Las Vegas, Harry Reid International Airport, and the Las Vegas Strip. Every unit is thoughtfully designed and equipped with its own garage and washer/dryer, offering a self-contained living experience for tenants. HOA takes care of the expenses related to trash, sewer, and water for the owners, lightening the financial burden. Tenants are responsible for their individual electricity bills, which are separately metered. Property to be sold "as-is".
